val day_of_the_day_UDF = udf { (day: String) => 
    day match {
        case "1" => "Monday"
        case "2" => "Tuesday"
        case "3" => "Wednesday"
        case "4" => "Thursday"
        case "5" => "Friday"
        case "6" => "Saturday"
        case "7" => "Sunday"
    }
}

spark.udf.register("day_of_the_day", day_of_the_day_UDF)

val non_empty_cols = Seq("YEAR", "MONTH", "DAY", "DAY_OF_WEEK", "AIRLINE", "FLIGHT_NUMBER", "TAIL_NUMBER", "ORIGIN_AIRPORT",

flights = flights.na.drop(non_empty_cols)
